Feb 17 (Reuters) - Tesla Inc (TSLA.O) has been weighing a takeover of battery metals miner Sigma Lithium Corp (SGML.V), Bloomberg News reported on Friday, citing people with knowledge of the matter. U.S.-listed shares of Sigma up 21% in trading after the bell. Tesla and Sigma Lithium did not immediately respond to Reuters requests for comment. Our Standards: The Thomson Reuters Trust Principles.